---
description: Helpful to avoid recent deprecations and general good practices
alwaysApply: false
---

-   Don't use legacy shadow style; use box shadow instead.
-   Always implement dark mode.
-   Don't use SafeAreaView from react-native since it's deprecated. Use SafeAreaView from react-native-safe-area-context instead.
-   Use contentinsetAdjustmentBehavior="automatic" with ScrollViews.
-   Each screen should use a ScrollView as its main container.
-   Avoid unnecessary comments.
-   Always apply styling using the nativewind / tailwind library.
-   Whenever necessary to add components from gluestack-ui add them automatically using the command `npx gluestack-ui add <component>`.
